name: Kota Factory
overview: In a city of coaching centers known to train India’s finest collegiate minds, an earnest but unexceptional student and his friends navigate campus life.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: In a city of coaching centers known to train India’s finest collegiate minds, an earnest but unexceptional student and his friends navigate campus life.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Continuing their pursuit of a coveted IIT seat, Vaibhav and his friends try not to let academic pressure — or adolescent angst — get the best of them.

episodes.name: Inventory
episodes.overview: Hoping to pass the IIT entrance exams, teen Vaibhav arrives in Kota with one goal: to nab a seat at the best coaching center in the city.

episodes.name: Assembly Line
episodes.overview: Canteen food, insomnia and studying weigh on Vaibhav, but when his friends’ tips don’t help, Professor Jeetu offers his campus-life survival strategies.

episodes.name: Optimization
episodes.overview: Struggling with Inorganic Chemistry, Vaibhav plots to have his instructor replaced, but his problem with the subject may not be the person teaching it.

episodes.name: Shutdown
episodes.overview: Given several days off before exams begin, Vaibhav, Meena and Uday each use the revision period to pursue romantic possibilities, with mixed results.

episodes.name: Overhaul
episodes.overview: Standing at a crossroads in his academic journey, Vaibhav is torn between his heart and his mind before making a big decision about his next steps.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: In a city of coaching centers known to train India’s finest collegiate minds, an earnest but unexceptional student and his friends navigate campus life.

episodes.name: Reasoning
episodes.overview: With their new classes off to a bleak start, Vaibhav and his peers question the value of the IIT dream and seek inspiration from a trusted source.

episodes.name: Control System
episodes.overview: Struggling with Physics, Vaibhav attempts to bend the rules to attend Jeetu’s classes. Meena frets that teenage hormones will get the best of him.

episodes.name: Atmospheric Pressure
episodes.overview: Jeetu searches for staff for his institute, making some reluctant choices along the way. Filled with self-doubt, Vartika evades practice tests at Aimers.

episodes.name: Repair & Maintenance
episodes.overview: When a bout of jaundice slows Vaibhav down in his studying, Jeetu insists he calls his only hope to get well quickly: his mother.

episodes.name: Packaging
episodes.overview: JEE results send Kota into celebration mode and give Vaibhav, Meena and Uday glimpses into their own futures, but the occasion comes with sad truths.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Continuing their pursuit of a coveted IIT seat, Vaibhav and his friends try not to let academic pressure — or adolescent angst — get the best of them.

episodes.name: Mission Statement
episodes.overview: Jeetu struggles to cope with the loss of a student. Vaibhav doubts his own path to success when his cricket-playing cousin visits Kota.

episodes.name: Fault Mitigation
episodes.overview: Facing financial stress, Meena begins tutoring an eager student to earn extra cash. Vaibhav's attitude forces Vartika to find a new study partner.

episodes.name: Benchmarking
episodes.overview: A clash with Gagan causes Jeetu to spiral. Shivangi feels the strain of the NEET prep, while Vaibhav and Meena compete for ranks in a test series.

episodes.name: Emergency Response
episodes.overview: Jeetu receives an offer that affects the future of Aimers. Uday’s error in judgment leads to serious trouble. Exam pressure takes its toll on Vaibhav.

episodes.name: Product Delivery
episodes.overview: Prayers and prep take hold as the final countdown to the exam approaches. Jeetu makes a startling announcement to his students.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: As the all-important exam nears, Jeetu and the students face an uphill challenge with ambition, loss and grueling pressure taking their toll.
